	<div id="blurb">
		<h3>Blurb</h3>
				<h4><a href="http://www.jejik.com/articles/2012/03/fix_ssh_login_delay/">Fix SSH login delay</a></h4>
			<p>When I google around for fixing SSH login delay, most articles tell you to add the <tt>UseDNS no</tt> you the server's <tt>sshd_config</tt> file. However, I regularly have to use some servers where this setting has been turned off but I still get delays. For future reference, here's my fix. Add the following to your client <tt>.ssh/config</tt>:</p>

<pre>
Host &lt;hostname&gt;
    GSSAPIAuthentication no
</pre>
			<div class="postinfo">
				Posted on 2012-03-09
